# Backend Controllers

- This project uses express
- Each endpoint should have openapi docs. This project uses swagger-jsdoc v6 to autogenerate open api doc.
- In swagger, describe the schema using `type:` instead of `$ref:`.
- Use [event.controller.js](mdc:src/controllers/event.controller.js) as reference

## Tests
- Tests for models should be atomic, dont use beforeEach and afterEach sections
- Use a `describe` section per endpoint
- Create tests for all endpoints in controller file
- The error response message is in `response.body.message` field
